Prerequisite:
1. Java 8 or higher
2. IDE: Eclipse or IntelliJ
3. Maven 

Steps to run:
1. Import the project as an Existing Maven project
2. Right click on project > Run as > Maven clean
3. Right click on project > Run as > Maven Install
4. Open BookInventoryManagementApplication.java
5. Right click and > Run as > Java Application
6. You can access the application from browser: http://localhost:8080/index.html

Assumptions:
1. Assumed to have in memory database to reduce further dependencies.
2. Pre-loaded few data records in Book table. That can be found in src/main/resources/data.sql